  "task_html": "\n<p>Du hast <strong>20 €</strong> in der Tasche. Welche Pizza bietet mehr Fläche pro Euro?</p>\n\n<div class=\"pizza-main-grid\">\n\n  <div class=\"pizza-visuals\">\n    <div class=\"pizza-card pizza-card-red\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 120 120\" class=\"pizza-svg\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n        <circle cx=\"60\" cy=\"60\" r=\"52\" fill=\"#f59e0b\" stroke=\"#92400e\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n        <circle cx=\"60\" cy=\"60\" r=\"44\" fill=\"#dc2626\" opacity=\".85\"/>\n        <circle cx=\"42\" cy=\"45\" r=\"5\" fill=\"#7f1d1d\"/>\n        <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"38\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#7f1d1d\"/>\n        <circle cx=\"55\" cy=\"68\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#7f1d1d\"/>\n        <circle cx=\"78\" cy=\"65\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#7f1d1d\"/>\n        <circle cx=\"38\" cy=\"70\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#7f1d1d\"/>\n        <line x1=\"8\" y1=\"60\" x2=\"112\" y2=\"60\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-dasharray=\"4,3\" opacity=\".7\"/>\n        <text x=\"60\" y=\"57\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"white\" font-family=\"monospace\" font-weight=\"bold\">Ø = 32 cm</text>\n      </svg>\n      <div class=\"pizza-name\">🍕 Salami</div>\n      <div class=\"pizza-info\">\n        <span class=\"pizza-size\">Ø <strong>32 cm</strong></span>\n        <span class=\"pizza-price\"><strong>7,99 €</strong></span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"pizza-card pizza-card-green\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 120 120\" class=\"pizza-svg\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n        <circle cx=\"60\" cy=\"60\" r=\"56\" fill=\"#f59e0b\" stroke=\"#92400e\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n        <circle cx=\"60\" cy=\"60\" r=\"48\" fill=\"#dc2626\" opacity=\".85\"/>\n        <circle cx=\"35\" cy=\"40\" r=\"5\" fill=\"#7f1d1d\"/>\n        <circle cx=\"65\" cy=\"30\" r=\"5\" fill=\"#7f1d1d\"/>\n        <circle cx=\"88\" cy=\"48\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#7f1d1d\"/>\n        <circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"60\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#7f1d1d\"/>\n        <circle cx=\"80\" cy=\"70\" r=\"5\" fill=\"#7f1d1d\"/>\n        <circle cx=\"38\" cy=\"78\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#7f1d1d\"/>\n        <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"85\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#7f1d1d\"/>\n        <line x1=\"4\" y1=\"60\" x2=\"116\" y2=\"60\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-dasharray=\"4,3\" opacity=\".7\"/>\n        <text x=\"60\" y=\"57\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"white\" font-family=\"monospace\" font-weight=\"bold\">Ø = 55 cm</text>\n      </svg>\n      <div class=\"pizza-name\">🍕 Familienpizza</div>\n      <div class=\"pizza-info\">\n        <span class=\"pizza-size\">Ø <strong>55 cm</strong></span>\n        <span class=\"pizza-price\"><strong>19,90 €</strong></span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"pizza-tasks\">\n    <div class=\"pizza-q-label\">Aufgabe</div>\n    <div class=\"pizza-q-list\" style=\"margin-bottom:14px;\">\n      <div class=\"pizza-q-item\"><span class=\"pizza-q-num\">a)</span><span>Berechne die Fläche beider Pizzen.</span></div>\n      <div class=\"pizza-q-item\"><span class=\"pizza-q-num\">b)</span><span>Berechne für jede Pizza: Wie viel cm² bekomme ich pro Euro?</span></div>\n      <div class=\"pizza-q-item\"><span class=\"pizza-q-num\">c)</span><span>Welche Pizza ist das bessere Angebot?</span></div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tbl-wrap\">\n      <table>\n        <thead><tr><th></th><th>🍕 Salami</th><th>🍕 Familie</th></tr></thead>\n        <tbody>\n          <tr>\n            <td class=\"row-label\">a) Fläche</td>\n            <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"804.25\" placeholder=\"? cm²\"></td>\n            <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"2375.83\" placeholder=\"? cm²\"></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td class=\"row-label\">b) cm² / €</td>\n            <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"100.7\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n            <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"119.4\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n\n    \n<div class=\"task-block task-orange\" style=\"margin-top:14px;\">\n  <div class=\"task-block-label\">c) Welche Pizza ist das bessere Angebot?</div>\n  <textarea style=\"width:100%;min-height:70px;padding:8px 10px;border:1.5px solid #fed7aa;border-radius:8px;font-size:13px;font-family:inherit;resize:vertical;\" placeholder=\"Begründe deine Antwort...\"></textarea>\n</div>\n<div class=\"check-bar\">\n      <button class=\"btn-check\" onclick=\"checkPizza()\">✓ Überprüfen</button>\n      <button class=\"btn-reset\" onclick=\"resetPizza()\">↺ Zurücksetzen</button>\n      <span class=\"check-result\" id=\"check-result-pizza\"></span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.pizza-main-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr;gap:20px;align-items:start;}\n@media(max-width:600px){.pizza-main-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}\n.pizza-visuals{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;}\n.pizza-tasks{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;}\n.pizza-card{border-radius:14px;padding:12px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:8px;border:2px solid;min-width:140px;}\n.pizza-card-red{background:#fff7ed;border-color:#fed7aa;}\n.pizza-card-green{background:#f0fdf4;border-color:#bbf7d0;}\n.pizza-svg{width:100px;height:100px;filter:drop-shadow(0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.18));}\n.pizza-name{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:var(--ink);}\n.pizza-info{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:3px;width:100%;}\n.pizza-size{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink2);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;}\n.pizza-price{font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:var(--accent);font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;}\n</style>\n",
  "sol_html": "\n<div class=\"pizza-sol\">\n  <div class=\"pizza-sol-item\">\n    <div class=\"pizza-sol-label\">a) Flächen</div>\n    <div class=\"pizza-sol-calc\">\n      Salami: A = π · 16² ≈ <strong>804,25 cm²</strong><br>\n      Familienpizza: A = π · 27,5² ≈ <strong>2375,83 cm²</strong>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pizza-sol-item\">\n    <div class=\"pizza-sol-label\">b) cm² pro Euro</div>\n    <div class=\"pizza-sol-calc\">\n      Salami: 804,25 ÷ 7,99 ≈ <strong>100,7 cm²/€</strong><br>\n      Familienpizza: 2375,83 ÷ 19,90 ≈ <strong>119,4 cm²/€</strong>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pizza-sol-item pizza-sol-winner\">\n    <div class=\"pizza-sol-label\">c) Fazit</div>\n    <div class=\"pizza-sol-calc\" style=\"font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;\">\n      🏆 Die <strong>Familienpizza</strong> – 119,4 cm²/€ gegenüber 100,7 cm²/€ bei der Salami.\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n"
}